'''2016年希拉自杀式卡车炸弹袭击'''是发生于2016年3月6日的一起[[自杀式炸弹袭击|自杀式炸弹袭击]]事件。袭击者将装满炸药的卡车撞向位于伊拉克[[巴格达|巴格达]]南部的城市[[希拉_(伊拉克)|希拉]]的一个安全检查站，炸死至少60人，另有70人受伤。[[伊斯兰国|伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国]]宣布对此次袭击负责。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A truck bomb killed 60 people in Iraq|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/03/iraq-deadly-suicide-attack-hits-highway-checkpoint-160306105957151.html|accessdate=6 March 2016|date=6 March 2016|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]]|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629081457/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/03/iraq-deadly-suicide-attack-hits-highway-checkpoint-160306105957151.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=60 people die in Iraq suicide truck bombing|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-35739729|accessdate=6 March 2016|date=6 March 2016|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918100434/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-35739729|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Suicide truck bombing left 60 dead in Iraq|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-blast-idUSKCN0W80G3|accessdate=6 March 2016|date=6 March 2016|publisher=Reuters|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306160012/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-blast-idUSKCN0W80G3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=60 people die in truck suicide bombing|url=https://www.rt.com/news/334700-suicide-bomb|accessdate=6 March 2016|date=6 March 2016|publisher=[[RT_(TV_network)|RT]]|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230233339/https://www.rt.com/news/334700-suicide-bomb/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2016/03/06/world/middleeast/ap-ml-iraq-the-latest.html?ref=world&_r=0|title=Suicide truck bombing killed 60 people in Hillah|work=The New York Times|date=6 March 2016|accessdate=6 March 2016}}</ref>

